content: The Knowledge base is currently disabled. To activate semantic search and document processing for AI agents, please contact your {{productName}} admin to configure the embeddings provider.

comment.text: This text explains to users that the knowledge base is currently disabled, preventing AI agents from using semantic search and document processing. It appears in a UI element (likely a container) informing the user to contact their administrator to enable the knowledge base. Translators should ensure the terminology "embeddings provider" is appropriately handled in the target language, as it's a technical term.
